## more maps / keybinds
### Unix
```
cmd open &$OPENER "$f"
map e $$EDITOR "$f"
map i $$PAGER "$f"
map w $$SHELL
cmd doc $$lf -doc | $PAGER
map <f-1> doc
cmd maps $lf -remote "query $id maps" | $PAGER
cmd cmaps $lf -remote "query $id cmaps" | $PAGER
cmd cmds $lf -remote "query $id cmds" | $PAGER
```

### Windows
```
cmd open &%OPENER% %f%
map e $%EDITOR% %f%
map i !%PAGER% %f%
map w $%SHELL%
cmd doc !%lf% -doc | %PAGER%
map <f-1> doc
cmd maps !%lf% -remote "query %id% maps" | %PAGER%
cmd cmaps !%lf% -remote "query %id% cmaps" | %PAGER%
cmd cmds !%lf% -remote "query %id% cmds" | %PAGER%
```

